    • Method Detail

      • generate

        public static BufferedImage generate(Object object,
                                     int imageSize)
        Generate a Identicon image based upon the provided Object instance.

        The object instance is hashed and a unique image is generated based upon the hash value.

        Parameters:
        object - the object to hash (is null safe)
        imageSize - the image horizontal and vertical size in pixels (default is 64)
        Returns:
        a rendered Identicon image

      • generate

        public static BufferedImage generate(Object object)
        Generate a Identicon image based upon the provided Object instance.

        The object instance is hashed and a unique image is generated based upon the hash value. The default image size of 64 pixels square is created.

        Parameters:
        object - the object to hash
        Returns:
        a rendered Identicon image (64 x 64 pixels)

      • getETag

        public static String getETag(Object object,

        Generate a ETag to correspond with the generated Identicon image based upon the provided Object instance.
        Parameters:
        object - the object to hash
        imageSize - the image horizontal and vertical size in pixels (default is 64)
        Returns:
        the Identicon image ETAG string
